630
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:50,060
I know he has a distrust of doctors, not of you.

631
00:34:57,290 --> 00:34:58,190
Where am I?

632
00:34:58,330 --> 00:35:00,940
You're in a hospital. You're okay.

633
00:35:03,420 --> 00:35:04,070
Eddie?

634
00:35:09,970 --> 00:35:10,870
Mary.

635
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,670
My lamb.

636
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:21,960
Daddy.

637
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,530
Shaun?

638
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,750
I meant what I said to Andrews.

639
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:59,040
He might never fully appreciate what you accomplished out there.

640
00:36:01,190 --> 00:36:02,090
But I did.

641
00:36:08,950 --> 00:36:09,800
I know.

642
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:16,980
Thank you, Shaun.

643
00:36:25,040 --> 00:36:26,530
Thank you, Jared.

644
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,630
Do you have my book?

645
00:37:30,110 --> 00:37:30,720
Yeah.

646
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:50,530
I said goodbye to Jared.

647
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:54,340
He has to go to Denver,

648
