649
00:37:58,260 --> 00:37:59,660
No you don't, Shaun.

650
00:38:03,810 --> 00:38:05,640
It's not up to Jared, it's not up to me,

651
00:38:05,650 --> 00:38:07,800
it's not to anyone to tell you where to be.

652
00:38:12,610 --> 00:38:13,430
I...

653
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:19,020
I've got a long journey ahead of me.

654
00:38:20,910 --> 00:38:25,060
And in the end, I've got to take it alone.

655
00:38:30,290 --> 00:38:32,780
Yes, I understand.

656
00:38:38,050 --> 00:38:39,370
I'm going with you.

657
00:39:14,630 --> 00:39:15,490
Jared.

658
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:34,090
