662
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:56,110
You know, I th... I think we made a mistake.

663
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,530
I made a mistake.

664
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:06,210
I'd like you to stay.

665
00:40:19,740 --> 00:40:20,470
No.

666
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:34,400
It's hard saying goodbye.

667
